This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it proposes a new deep convolutional neural network for fast visual style transfer. It also involves modifications to the cost function to achieve photorealistic results, which could fall under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the structure of the gradient descent, which could be relevant to Graphics (cs.GR) and Multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
